{"tid":553981,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[無限之戰]最強奸角媲美黑武士 　導演：滅霸係今集主角","createTime":"2018-02-08T05:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T15:41:36.000Z","uid":105567,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9040af83c0bd8c672cd0744b1c6fb4f7933e33b7","tid":553981,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/電影/152195/-復仇者聯盟3-最強奸角媲美黑武士-導演-滅霸係今集主角\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%2F152195%2F-%E5%BE%A9%E4%BB%87%E8%80%85%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F3-%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E5%A5%B8%E8%A7%92%E5%AA%B2%E7%BE%8E%E9%BB%91%E6%AD%A6%E5%A3%AB-%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94-%E6%BB%85%E9%9C%B8%E4%BF%82%E4%BB%8A%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%BB%E8%A7%92&d=G8A4%2Btb3AoGxh5fllcsGhP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=baa9eb43\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/電影/152195/-復仇者聯盟3-最強奸角媲美黑武士-導演-滅霸係今集主角</a><br />\n<br />\n萬眾期待的《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》（Avengers: Infinity War）仲有3個月先上映，片中集結過往10年Marvel各路超級英雄，誰人佔最多戲分仍是未知之數，但導演之一Joe Russo最近受訪透露，堪稱Marvel最強奸角的「滅霸」（Thanos）才是這部電影的主角，比鐵甲奇俠及美國隊長等更搶鏡：「《復仇者聯盟3》是滅霸的電影。」<br />\n<br />\nJoe Russo表示，小時候認為《星球大戰》的「黑武士」（Darth Vader）是他心目中最勁抽的奸角，希望將滅霸打造成新一代的黑武士：「我們希望滅霸能令觀眾由心產生恐懼，亦希望大家與滅霸一同經歷」。早前Marvel公開的官方預告片中，並沒有收錄去年暑假於聖地牙哥動漫節中曝光的滅霸掟走月球畫面，Joe Russo謂掟月球只是滅霸其中一件壯舉，仲有好多大場面未公開，相信屆時觀眾看到這位貌似布斯韋利士（Bruce Willis）的大奸角比一眾超級英雄還多。"},{"pid":"dcb9f3989e28c2077dbace2de321670aa4742db8","tid":553981,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T05:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f7926d50d28d11ff6458bd72655fa90b0613c1","tid":553981,"uid":11962,"like":5,"dislike":19,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T05:37:30.000Z","msg":"獻醜不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4355aee8836c8de1ba821c11553a003dfc212e6","tid":553981,"uid":126044,"like":7,"dislike":13,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T09:51:50.000Z","msg":"個look 好柒<br />\n<br />\nSteppenwolf 型過thanos 多多聲"},{"pid":"b9b5aea340fb23e1031b33127ac7f72299a85d51","tid":553981,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T10:21:34.000Z","msg":"相信屆時觀眾看到這位貌似布斯韋利士（Bruce Willis）的大奸角比一眾超級英雄還多。<br />\njosh brolin表示:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3eae376700d1562af9e1d5e51c483408b18341d","tid":553981,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T10:24:36.000Z","msg":"掟走月球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a87e889cc3d94ab4df9bb5f25613061f3b33604","tid":553981,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5b7aa2ba1ac8c0825fead290d8861b8350e88d","tid":553981,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:20:53.000Z","msg":"啪一啪手指 宇宙死一半"},{"pid":"063e5ffcba04597321258720f45cb29dfc63d3ef","tid":553981,"uid":167426,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d4355aee8836c8de1ba821c11553a003dfc212e6","tid":553981,"uid":126044,"like":7,"dislike":13,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T09:51:50.000Z","msg":"個look 好柒<br />\n<br />\nSteppenwolf 型過thanos 多多聲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:29:00.000Z","msg":"你話thanos 個look 好柒我都認同<br />\n但你竟然搵個更柒嘅嚟比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2fd9baa1f1391c940658502cfecd6ec38c71e6","tid":553981,"uid":16917,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T15:31:13.000Z","msg":"有冇人同我一樣睇錯波霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br 